ing, they'll have to confront the past before they can embrace the beautiful possibilities of the future"--Provided by publisher. 0aWeddingsvFiction. 0aWomen dressmakersvFiction. 0aWedding costumevFiction. 0aFamily secretsvFiction. 0aGenerationsvFiction. 0aLarge type books. 7aDomestic fiction.2lcgft 7aHistorical fiction.2lcgft  c(OCoLC)1137853992  c4493d4493